Scheduler
=========

SOPE based interface for scheduler.

Class Hierarchy
===============

  [WOComponent]
    [SoComponent]
      UIxAppointmentView
      UIxCalView
        UIxCalMonthViewOld
          UIxCalMonthOverview
        UIxCalMonthView
        UIxCalWeekView
          UIxCalWeekOverview
            UIxCalWeekPrintview
          UIxCalWeekColumnsview
          UIxCalWeekListview
          UIxCalWeekChartview
        UIxCalDayView
          UIxCalDayOverview
          UIxCalDayChartview
    UIxAptTableView
  SchedulerUIProduct

TBD:
